channel.description:

ive been search for about an hour or two and its not clicking for me but im going to keep looking. if anone can help i would appreciate it =D?

item.title: Need help finding a starter server
item.dc:creator: @RiiPiiNFtW RiiPiiNFtW
item.description:
@RiiPiiNFtW wrote:

There are so many servers like you described, they just don’t look like they contain it. Just try a PI, no Delta please, and program it to your liking. The things you want woulden’t take much time to code in if they weren’t already there.
